                    <div class="ice-badge">ICE/HOT</div>
                </div>
                <div class="menu-info">
                    <h3>아메리카노</h3>
                    <p>깊은 풍미의 에스프레소와 물의 조화</p>
                    <span class="price">4,500원</span>
                    <div class="menu-details">
                        <div class="nutrition-info">
                            <div class="nutrition-item">
                                <span>용량</span>
                                <span>450ml</span>
                            </div>
                            <div class="nutrition-item">
                                <span>칼로리</span>
                                <span>10kcal</span>
                            </div>
                            <div class="nutrition-item">
                                <span>카페인</span>
                                <span>150mg</span>
